headline: DTE Energy price target raised to $135 from $125 at BMO Capital
summary: BMO Capital raised the firm’s price target on DTE Energy (DTE) to $135 from $125 and keeps a Market Perform rating on the shares after its Q4 earnings beat. The firm is also more confident in the management’s ability to deliver growth at the higher end of its 6%-8% growth outlook, the analyst tells investors in a research note.
